{"word":"προποιέω","slug":"προποιέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προποιέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to do before</i> or <i>beforehand</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <el>προποιῆσαι</el> <i>to make the first move</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to prepare beforehand</i>, plup. <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>προεπεποίητο</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}